Breathe taking!
This place gave me goosebumps it was so beautiful. Inside the pagoda were monks chanting which echoed through the main area after the steep climb to the entrance. Make sure you wear suitable clothing as there are lots of steep stairs and caves to climb. Stunning views of the ocean and surrounds.
